.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH px2ansi-rs-convert 1  "px2ansi-rs-convert " 
.SH NAME
px2ansi\-rs\-convert \- Convert a single image to ANSI/Unicode/Fade/Braille/Kanji/Full\-block/Ascii
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpx2ansi\-rs\-convert\fR [\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-O\fR|\fB\-\-output\-image\fR] [\fB\-\-style\fR] [\fB\-\-density\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-color\fR] [\fB\-\-width\fR] [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-filter\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIINPUT\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Convert a single image to ANSI/Unicode/Fade/Braille/Kanji/Full\-block/Ascii
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR
Output file (optional)
.TP
\fB\-O\fR, \fB\-\-output\-image\fR \fI<OUTPUT_IMAGE>\fR
Save a rasterized preview instead of terminal escape codes
.TP
\fB\-\-style\fR \fI<STYLE>\fR

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
ansi
.IP \(bu 2
unicode
.IP \(bu 2
braille
.IP \(bu 2
fade
.IP \(bu 2
ascii
.IP \(bu 2
full\-block
.IP \(bu 2
dense
.IP \(bu 2
kanji
.IP \(bu 2
chinese
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-density\fR \fI<DENSITY>\fR
Character density for \-\-style ascii and \-\-style fade. Light: sparse 30\-char ramp, Medium: full 92\-char ramp, Heavy: block\-heavy ramp
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
medium
.IP \(bu 2
light
.IP \(bu 2
heavy
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-color\fR
Disable ANSI color output (monochrome). Applies to ascii, fade, braille, kanji, and chinese modes
.TP
\fB\-\-width\fR \fI<WIDTH>\fR
Force a specific width
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-filter\fR \fI<FILTER>\fR
Nearest is best for pixel art. Lanczos3 is best for high\-resolution images.
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
nearest: Nearest Neighbor (Best for pixel art)
.IP \(bu 2
triangle: Linear interpolation
.IP \(bu 2
catmull\-rom: Sharp cubic filter
.IP \(bu 2
gaussian: Blurry cubic filter
.IP \(bu 2
lanczos3: High\-quality resampling (Slowest)
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
<\fIINPUT\fR>
Input image file
